Collectors.summarizingInt()
Ek Line Definition

Ek hi Stream se Count + Sum + Average + Min + Max sab ek saath nikalna ho to summarizingInt() use karte hain.

Ye production me reports aur dashboards banane ke liye bahut use hota hai.

Problem

Suppose tumhare paas students ke marks hain.

Rahul  80
Amit   65
Neha   90
Riya   70
Ankit  85

Ab manager bolta hai

Total Students

Total Marks

Average Marks

Highest Marks

Lowest Marks

Purane Java me

int sum = 0;
int max = Integer.MIN_VALUE;
int min = Integer.MAX_VALUE;

for(Student s : students){
    sum += s.getMarks();

    if(s.getMarks() > max)
        max = s.getMarks();

    if(s.getMarks() < min)
        min = s.getMarks();
}

double average = (double)sum / students.size();

Bahut code.

Java 8 ne bola

Ek Collector se sab de deta hu.